---
title: Yellow Cod Thai Curry with Lime Rice Three Steps | Ready in 10
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Yellow Cod Thai Curry in just 10 minutes for a balanced and tasty meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/yellow-cod-thai-curry-de07ebde-aedd3819.jpg
